        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          More than just a tour operator - we're your safari partners
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">ğŸ’°</div>
